snR61-SNORD38
=============

- snR61_intronic-boxCDsnoRNA-83nt-in-CNL04930
- Within 1\ :sup:`st` intron of CNL04930 (CNAG_07813) for transcription initiation factor TFIID subunit 13
- Predicted target in |targetRNA|\ : |target|
- Orthologue of |ortholog|
- Accessory guide (\ |extr|\ ) is conserved in fungi [van.Nues-2011_]

SNORD17
=======

- SNORD17_intronic-boxCDsnoRNA-83nt-in-CNL04930
- Within 2\ :sup:`nd` intron of CNL04930 (CNAG_07813) for transcription initiation factor TFIID subunit 13
- Possible target in |targetRNA-2|\ : |target-2|
- Orthologue of |ortholog-2|
- Placement of C' box is tentative
- Role of the conserved element |extr2| is unclear; of the many sections with complimetarity (\ |extr2-target|) none is near the putative base-pairing site (\ |target-2|) in the primary or the secondary structure of the mature rRNA
- In yeast, with HACA snoRNA snR86_ the targeted nucleotide is converetd into a pseudouridine
